<p>On the line, she said: 'I feel so excited and lucky to be still working with PrettyLittleThing one year on and creating collections that I absolutely love.'</p>

<p>Praising the brand values, she went on: 'I love everything that PLT stands for and it's amazing to be bringing out another Edit with them.'  </p>

